Description¶

The objective of this dataset is to help predict if a person male
 or female has type 1, type 2, or has no diabetes. The variables include
 Gender, Age, Heart Disease, Smoking_History, BMI, Hba1c Levels,and
 Blood Glucose Levels with an outcome variable of Diabetes

df['Gender'] = df['Gender'].astype('category').cat.codes
print('\nGender is converted to integer:\n{}'.format(df['Gender'].value_counts()))


print('Smoking_History is originally a string variable:\n{}'.format(df['Smoking_History'].value_counts()))
df['Smoking_History'] = df['Smoking_History'].astype('category').cat.codes
print('\nSmoking_History is converted to integer:\n{}'.format(df['Smoking_History'].value_counts()))
